      <title>贷方称无美元支付系统将为非洲节省 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/no-dollar-payment-system-to-save-africa-5-billion-lender-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲最大银行的商业银行业务主管表示，在非洲跨境交易中取消美元支付的支付系统可以为非洲节省高达 50 亿美元的处理成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/no-dollar-payment-system-to-save-africa-5-billion-lender-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 06:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰通胀和预算赤字将维持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polish-inflation-budget-deficit-keep-interest-rates-on-hold-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀加速和预算赤字扩大的背景下，波兰可能会延长暂停加息的时间，投资者正在等待央行关于何时开始实施宽松政策的新指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/polish-inflation-budget-deficit-keep-interest-rates-on-hold-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场预期特朗普胜选，新兴货币暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场货币下跌，因为交易员预计唐纳德·特朗普将赢得美国总统大选，这一结果被视为将提振美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师认为美国民意调查结果将影响中国股市和美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/analysts-see-us-poll-results-affecting-chinese-stocks-us-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师认为，中国股市、美元、日元和韩元是最有可能受到美国大选结果影响的资产之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/analysts-see-us-poll-results-affecting-chinese-stocks-us-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
