    <item>
      <title>特朗普在美国总统选举中领先，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-rises-to-highest-since-july-as-polls-close-in-key-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统竞选中领先，美元上涨，引发美国国债收益率大幅上升，因为市场猜测他的政策将使美国利率维持在高位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/dollar-rises-to-highest-since-july-as-polls-close-in-key-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 02:21:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普交易助推美元上涨 油价回落 美国计票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普赢得总统大选的可能性不断增加，美元上涨，同时一份行业报告显示美国库存增加，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在美国大选中领先，美元上涨，黄金持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统大选中取得领先，黄金价格稳定，美元飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普交易势头强劲，美国股市和收益率上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球范围内与唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 总统竞选前景上升有关的一系列交易取得了决定性的进展，股指期货延续涨势，美国国债收益率跃升，美元创下 2023 年 2 月以来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元延续跌势，特朗普竞选活动推进，日本股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/japanese-stock-futures-edge-higher-before-us-votes-tallied</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统大选的早期结果导致一些交易员押注唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 比卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 更具优势，日本蓝筹股指数上涨逾 3%，而日元跌至 7 月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/japanese-stock-futures-edge-higher-before-us-votes-tallied</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 22:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其公司考虑卢布互换以缓解受制裁影响的贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/turkey-launching-ruble-swap-to-ease-trade-squeezed-by-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家土耳其天然气贸易商正在开展货币兑换业务，以简化俄罗斯和土耳其之间的未经批准的贸易，这表明企业正在寻找解决支付问题的创造性方法，同时为中间商创造有利可图的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/turkey-launching-ruble-swap-to-ease-trade-squeezed-by-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 14:49:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
